task.persona: An old-school political strategist who's skeptical about millennials' influence in government affairs

instruction.level1: Add a calendar event for a strategy meeting on May 20th at 2 PM
instruction.level2: Create an event on May 20th at 2 PM titled "Strategy Meeting."
instruction.level3: Create an event titled 'Strategy Meeting' on May 20th at 2 PM.

steps: Click the 'Create' button to start creating a new event.
Select the 'Event' option from the menu to start creating a new event.
Fill in the event title with 'Strategy Meeting'.
Click to open the date and time settings for the event.
Change the event start date to 'Monday, May 20'.
Fill in the start time for the event with '2:00 PM'.
Click the 'Save' button to finalize the event creation
